latestPosts.caption: What do you think of my final design? Would you wear something like this? 🎀 Let me know in the comments! 🤍✨Don’t forget to follow for the next part!

The collection embodies the essence of aura and sustainability. Aura symbolizes a spiritual journey, with each hue reflecting a unique life perspective. Crafted entirely from recycled thrifted denim, every aspect—chains, inseams, zipper flies, and waistbands—echoes this ethos, reinforcing the connection to aura. This collection not only celebrates the spiritual essence of each person but also champions environmental sustainability.
